data.Name: Highly Suspect
data.Bio: A rock music trio from Massachusetts that started in 2009 as a cover band. Since their formation they have played over 800 live shows, and have released four full length albums, their self-titled album Highly Suspect (2011), Mister Asylum (2015), The Boy Who Died Wolf (2016) and MCID (2019). In addition to this, they've released three EPs: The Gang Lion EP (2010), The Worst Humans (2012), Black Ocean EP (2013). Read more on Last.fm
